member.name: E:ATCOMM.Phone.Phone.NewDeliveryReport
member.remarks: ''' The NewDeliveryReport Event is raised whenever a delivery report is raised for a previously sent text message with delivery status report request, if DeliveryReport property is set as True. If a message was sent with LongMessage property is set as EnumLongMessage.Concatenate then delivery status report will be received only for the last of all the part messages. The NewDeliveryReport event is raised on a secondary thread when a new delivery report is received.
